remove(T) - Method in class Custom_CollectionsED.list.arrayLists.ArrayList
The remove method : check if the arrayList is empty; iterates through the entire array looking to find the index of the element given as a parameter in the array; after finding the index for the element to be removed, proceeds to move all element in the array one spot to the right, beginning at the index of the element to be removed, thus eliminating it from the array; turns the last spot in the array into null ( eliminating duplicates for the last element ); updates the counter variable; updates the modCount variable;
